ue\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dgv1665702916539.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dgv1665702916539.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dgv1665702916539.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dgv1665702916539\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Translate an error code to a text.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__section_mp5_q5w_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d967115e50\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__p_d130352e1_d130353e1_d130354e1\">Provide Uniface with a string that contains the error\n        message text corresponding to a connector error code or a DBMS error code.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__p_d130355e1_d130356e1_d130357e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">Message</code> request must be\n        successful, if necessary, by supplying a default error message.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__section_s1p_n4x_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d967115e65\">From Uniface</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Available Uniface information for the <code class=\"ph codeph\">Message</code> request.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Information Available from Uniface</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__1\">Data Structure-&gt;Element </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__2\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrverr</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__2\">Error code to be translated. This is a code that has\n                been supplied to Uniface by the connector itself in\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrverr</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrvini</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__2\">Unique identification of the current logon\n                path.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;iobuf</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__2\">Points to the general I/O buffer.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;sqlbuf</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__2\">Points to the SQL buffer.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrvnum</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15563e1_d15564e1_d15565e1__entry__2\">Connector sequence number.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__section_dxx_n4x_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d967115e160\">To Uniface</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__p_d130364e1_d130365e1_d130366e1\">The connector request return value must be 0. Do not\n        change the value of <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrverr</code>. The error message must be stored as\n        a null-terminated string of printable ASCII characters in the general I/O buffer. The\n        message length is only limited by the size of the general I/O buffer.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15566e1_d15567e1_d15568e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Connector Request Return Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15566e1_d15567e1_d15568e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15566e1_d15567e1_d15568e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15566e1_d15567e1_d15568e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15566e1_d15567e1_d15568e1__entry__2\">Success</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15566e1_d15567e1_d15568e1__entry__1\">-9</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dgv1665702916539__table_d15566e1_d15567e1_d15568e1__entry__2\">I/O server logon error.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__section_hrd_w5w_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d967115e218\">Service functions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Not applicable.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__section_cfd_t5w_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d967115e227\">Extra information</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__p_d130376e1_d130377e1_d130378e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">Message</code> request can be provided\n        with a dummy control block. This control block does not describe a table and it does not\n        have an associated connector workspace.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dgv1665702916539__p_d130379e1_d130380e1_d130381e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">Message</code> request can be called\n        without a current logon path (<code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrvini = 0</code>).</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azl1665702915888.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uctrl</a><p>Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526806\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526806\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Message ('M') Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Translate an error code to a text. Description Provide Uniface with a string that contains the error message text corresponding to a connector error code or a DBMS error code. The Message request must be successful, if necessary, by supplying a default error message. From Uniface Available Uniface information for the Message request. Table 1. Information Available from Uniface Data Structure->Element Description uctrl->udrverr Error code to be translated. This is a code that has been supplied to Uniface by the connector itself in uctrl->udrverr . uctrl->udrvini Unique identification of the current logon path. uctrl->iobuf Points to the general I/O buffer. uctrl->sqlbuf Points to the SQL buffer. uctrl->udrvnum Connector sequence number. To Uniface The connector request return value must be 0. Do not change the value of uctrl->udrverr . The error message must be stored as a null-terminated string of printable ASCII characters in the general I/O buffer. The message length is only limited by the size of the general I/O buffer. Table 2. Connector Request Return Values Value Description 0 Success -9 I/O server logon error. Service functions Not applicable. Extra information The Message request can be provided with a dummy control block. This control block does not describe a table and it does not have an associated connector workspace. The Message request can be called without a current logon path ( uctrl->udrvini = 0 ). Related Links uctrl Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}